Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations for the shuttle\Nlaunch are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:46.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Countdown will commence immediately\Nfollowing the Valkyrie unit launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:57.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,In an effort to bolster military readiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.45,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,a plan was devised to capture the\NZentradi Factory Satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:02.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,an automated plant for the\Nconstruction of space vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:09.66,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the soldiers from Earth participating\Nin this operation are preparing for liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch the shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:54.39,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,142)}VIVA MARIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:47.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Britai, I'm glad to see you're looking well, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Exsedol! You're looking well yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Major LaSalle, Major Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think of my ship as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Commander Britai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:06.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Exsedol? I've gotten quite\Ngood at Earth greetings myself, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show you to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How goes the loading\Nof our human guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All finished, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Begin preparations for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since my last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:09.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never could have imagined\Nthat my next one would be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,a joint operation between us and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this too the power of culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uprisings have been breaking out\Nall over and... Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:26.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, you have to clean\Nthe pus from the wound, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since we've\Nbeen on this ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, not since we were taken prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:35.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we ex-prisoners throw a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can invite Claudia too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:41.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to show Milia what\Nan Earth-style house party is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What would we do for food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:48.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese, European, Chinese...\NI'll take any requests you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're practically Superman, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reactor output green.\NEnergy level is 9.5 and climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calculation of space-fold\Ncoordinates complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All systems ready for long-range fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:06.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Commence fold navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Milia, could I hold Komilia for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:40.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hold a baby, why don't\Nyou make one of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia, that's not a very nice way to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:50.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Major Hayase hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Major, here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I never...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like she's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Komilia's got\Na very strong skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how could you bring a baby\Nalong to a battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can protect my own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be capable on the battlefield,\Nbut that doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not shy around new people at all, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure isn't! Let me hold her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I had her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Komilia, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I made her laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Milia getting angry that they\Nwon't give Komilia back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:59.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry. That's the look\Nof a woman who's happy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that her baby's getting so much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, isn't Miss Hayase the one\Nyou should be worrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:10.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! See how happy she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:11.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She really loves babies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she'd be even happier\Nif that were her baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to see her\Nwith a baby of her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit lookin' at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on over there?\NSecret guy talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, and women aren't allowed to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I'm jealous!\NCome on over here, Milia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We women will just liven things up on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:43.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Just like the good old\Ndays in the Zentradi army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:01.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a great time today!\NMax's cooking was terrific too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:04.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You had fun because you got\Nto hold Komilia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\NI guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come in for some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think I'll call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, I'm going to walk\NClaudia to her quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me inside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you holding Komilia...\NIt suited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:59.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roy, I never got to hold your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I didn't mean to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least put some\Ntea on while you waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it slipped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Komilia sure was adorable, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you've been talking\Nabout since we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it that you don't like babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.\NI like babies just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:11:00.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to change the topic, but there's something\NI've wanted to ask you for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Majors Hayase and LaSalle, please\Nreport to the bridge immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:16.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, let's talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Commander Britai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an Earth ship and it doesn't\Nlook like a Zentradi type either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, that is a\NSupervision Army warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I surmise that the ship was recently destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After the remainder of Bodolzaa's\Nfleet had scattered?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, let's conduct a more\Ndetailed investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:08.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the second contact between\Nthe Earth and the Supervision Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already provided you with all our\Ninformation on the Supervision Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a new source of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:23.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that it's not a\Nbooby trap like the Macross was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When you consider the importance of\Nthis mission we must take no risks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how slight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:32.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, Archivist Exsedol is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence final fold at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:27.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Protoculture must have been incredibly\Npowerful to build something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Recon mission, ready to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not giving you\Nyour instructions sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are cleared to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me Commander Dagao of the garrison fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:42.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your plan, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd advise him to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:53.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, knowing how hardheaded he is,\NI doubt it will do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't "advising" him to\Nsurrender a little too soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we prove that we're the\NProtoculture, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What do you think, Exsedol?\NAny good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a "kiss" would probably be most effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly produces quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase, would you do as you did\Nwhen you were a prisoner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately... Captain\NIchijo, wasn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That soldier should be on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Misa.\NYou're doing it for the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so you might as well put on a big show!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:38.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have Commander Dagao.\NI'll put him on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Britai.\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:46.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I demand that you surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You demand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, what can you do\Nwith a single ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made contact with the Protoculture\Nand now possess culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your best interest to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru Ichijo, reporting for duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Dagao, please observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the reason for\Nthose miclones being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me they are the Protocult...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... That's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. A woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:20.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These two will now demonstrate a tiny\Nsliver of the power of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of culture? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he mean what I think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:34.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell me something like that and\Nexpect me to just go, "Oh, really? Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Captain Ichijo takes\Nobjection to this strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:43.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He can object all he wants, but\NMajor Hayase has already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, this is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no choice but to kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why does Captain Ichijo hate kissing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do it in front of everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your superior officer is giving you an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty high-handed for a CO to\Norder a subordinate to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overstepping your authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.61,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.40,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:17.14,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,With him after school, on my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? What is that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen! Don't listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:23.85,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the corner of that same old intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dagao! You should see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:29.09,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,He made sure no one else was around
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:34.82,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then without warning, he kissed me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:41.18,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was so angry, I led him to think
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look! Do not look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.16,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck, Britai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.07,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was dizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.15,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,and my heart was fluttering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think a trick like that\Nwould work on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.63,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about Protoculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.00,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Four, three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.52,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miclones! The miclones are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Milia and Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:12.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:18.34,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To that blue, shining world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:24.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:29.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you please
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:33.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am former Zentradi soldier, Milia Fallyna Jenius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Milia from the Lap'Lamiz Fleet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:42.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is Maximilian Fallyna Jenius\Nof the Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a miclone.\NWhat's so great about Protoculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,If war is our destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Protoculture miclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:06.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Then war is our life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called a "baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Komilia Maria Fallyna Jenius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.65,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Never look back. Never stop
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll gradually grow larger until\Nshe is the same size as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us created her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:15.61,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And never forget your pride
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can defeat the Protoculture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:21.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:27.47,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely! This is the sign of the Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:33.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,let me be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be contaminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:38.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you please
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:55.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like one Komilia had more impact\Nthan the two of you kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:19:00.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't destroyed\Ntheir flagship, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling how they'll react.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will prepare for battle, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:05.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:09.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one is to sortie unless\Nthe enemy attacks first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie squadron, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Squadron, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?!\NHurry up and destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The men are mutinying! I can't control them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mutineers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying that all ships contaminated\Nby the Protoculture must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is in total disarray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the chance to take out\Nas many of them as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another enemy warship has been\Nrendered inoperable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire main batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:51.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is the enemy ship dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:56.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Queadluun-Rau squadron,\Nyou are in our line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get clear immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire main batteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:33.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've accepted us as the Protoculture, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:37.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with the captured\Nenemy soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They too are our brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them that any who wish to\Njoin us won't be turned away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations are more or less ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way of knowing if it\Nwill stand up to repeated folds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:23.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Irrelevant. Commence activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:24.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy levels are at 20.7 and rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:32.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fold coordinates are plotted and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:35.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations for long-range fold are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:37.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All fold systems to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:59.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In one minute, we will de-fold\Nat the Lagrange Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:01.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fold system is almost at its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:05.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've reached our destination,\NI'm not sure we can use it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:08.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we've achieved\Nour primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find some way to cover our tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are de-folding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.25,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(86,104)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.25,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,457)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentradi are on the rampage in Trad City
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:42.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're planning to steal a micloning device.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:45.51,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru and his men race to the scene and\Nwhile they are able to quell the offensive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:49.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,they are unable to hand the device\Nover to the New UN Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:55.38,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, Kamujin's war machines\Nattack the city once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:58.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:23:59.62,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"SATAN'S DOLLS"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.38,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(68,125)}SATAN'S DOLLS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:23.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:29.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:36.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.75,0:24:44.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:51.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:56.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:15.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
